{"tid":1857764,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"幫襯完楊明哥哥嘅燉湯之後開始出現病徵...","createTime":"2020-02-02T10:23:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T22:33:56.000Z","uid":132174,"like":76,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"69adb64a98f3119b1b1848786394c8a7c0c9a61f","tid":1857764,"uid":132174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:23:43.000Z","msg":"本身諗住去楊明哥哥嗰度飲碗靚湯<br />\n順邊攞個免費口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n店入面生意依然好旺 要等成三個字先入到去<br />\n亦都聽到有啲街坊讚陽明哥哥派口罩係個英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪太忙碌嘅關係 店入面好多阿姐都冇戴口罩<br />\n我嘆緊碗靚湯個時發現有個侍應阿姐係咁咳<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咳咳下仲噴晒啲血落去人哋碗花膠魚翅湯度<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連浙江醋都慳返<br />\n<br />\n咁我見狀梗係醒啦 即刻埋單走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知前日開始發高燒同不停咳 啱啱仲發現有啲血絲 有冇人可以話俾我聽點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8e3b0a05e555e26ddea7e435e5d909e7d7759c","tid":1857764,"uid":256393,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:25:10.000Z","msg":"去警署報失"},{"pid":"288fd5105f901b88de7b6f0bd2d55c61619555c2","tid":1857764,"uid":259901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:26:31.000Z","msg":"幫警署嗌加醋外賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee046aef667720b5490ac302c6ee70572498fb86","tid":1857764,"uid":127177,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c8e3b0a05e555e26ddea7e435e5d909e7d7759c","tid":1857764,"uid":256393,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:25:10.000Z","msg":"去警署報失"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-02T10:28:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor